commitResults.messageTitle: TaskList: Fix methods to work based on task number
commitResults.messageBody:
Currently, all commands still modify tasks based on their index in the
array list instead of their assigned task number. This commit fixes this
mistake. And change all instances of task index to task number because
index sounds misleading.

Also some minor changes to the formatting by removing redundant empty
or new lines.
